{"tid":1310243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請向鄉事局成員認清邊個先係你地既敵人","createTime":"2019-07-12T14:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T14:52:46.000Z","uid":20003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1435bd05b499340aeef8eca9cef190818b9d74b5","tid":1310243,"uid":20003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:46:47.000Z","msg":"2012年，時任發展局長林鄭月娥指出新界原居民之丁權，不能無限期維持下去，建議2047年後停止丁屋政策，以2029年為劃界線，之後出生之新界男丁不再享有丁權[7]。<br />\n<br />\n2013年9月12日，《大公報》認為大量內地來港新移民蜂擁而入不是造成香港住房短缺的主要原因，而是香港現有住房問題很大程度上是由於新界原居民大量非法佔用土地，以及受到「新界小型屋宇」政策的影響[8]。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/新界小型屋宇政策\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B%E5%B1%8B%E5%AE%87%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=ead1ab2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/新界小型屋宇政策</a>"},{"pid":"5c7da4f253db700e5f8b8a5a407c31b470a63017","tid":1310243,"uid":20003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee254d763cf14b41c52ca48625b2d87dbe2a7484","tid":1310243,"uid":20003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db69069ebf1e4ed4af507a8b8a0c8f0c33262b47","tid":1310243,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"共產黨根本最憎地主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1663ddc6cd07569951725b813863104fac98907","tid":1310243,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"牛屎佬只係見到眼前利益"}]}